SYS:Utilities/Installer
#.HTML
TOOLS:Comm/MoreHTML/MoreHTML
ascii
WORK:Bin/MuchMore
amigaguide
SYS:Utilities/PowerGuide PUBSCREEN=Workbench
#.CDXL
WORK:Bin/CDgsXL
#.ANIM
PIC:CyberAnim/CyberAnim
#.FLI
PIC:Flick/Flick
#.FLC
PIC:Flick/Flick
#.AVI
WORK:Bin/TapAVI
#.MPEG
WORK:Bin/AmiPeg
#.movie
WORK:Bin/MoviePlayer
#.MOV
WORK:Bin/QT
#.ANMB
WORK:Bin/VT
